name: GlobalClashResolutionStrategy

properties.name: LOAD_ALL_WITH_OVERWRITE
properties.description: Overwrites existing styles whose names clash with imported items.

properties.name: LOAD_ALL_WITH_RENAME
properties.description: Renames imported styles whose names clash with existing items to preserve existing items.

properties.name: DO_NOT_LOAD_THE_STYLE
properties.description: Does not import styles whose names clash with existing items.

description: The resolution strategy to employ for imported styles that have the same names as existing styles.
